Oh yes, just small presents and - I just remember one birthday party I had. And we got a special new tea service for the occasion I remember. I don't know what age I was. About - perhaps eleven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3021308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Would you have anything special to eat for the birthday tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6029762 GC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Oh yes, but I can't remember what but it was a special birthday tea you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3021308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Would you have any little friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6029762 GC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Yes, and there were little friends there as well.
