Christmas Day. Well we certainly used to get presents, I've come downstairs and have stockings hanging on the bedrail you know. With usually an appl
e and orange in the toe and - and nuts you know, if there were nuts. But we did used to have Christmas - that way and of course there was the usual Christmas - at church. And the Christmas tree, we had a Christmas tree.
