\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3021308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Would you sing carols on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6029762 GC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3021308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6029762 GC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Just the piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3021308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Who were the players of the piano?
