t nature but - other than that I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3021308 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864503\charrsid2561303 Would you get this magazine regularly?
